&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;A critical and distinctive part of this role is building and owning the custodian playbook — a comprehensive, per-custodian operational guide that standardizes how Vestmark onboards new clients, configures integrations, and supports day-to-day operations across each custodial relationship.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Equally important is serving as the&amp;nbsp;Vestmark&amp;nbsp;champion for making&amp;nbsp;it easier for advisors to do business with Vestmark, by ensuring that custodian infrastructure and Vestmark&#39;s platform capabilities are seamlessly connected.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is a highly cross-functional role that sits at the intersection of relationship management, technical program delivery, and operational coordination. The ideal candidate brings equal&amp;nbsp;parts&amp;nbsp;relationship acumen and technical&amp;nbsp;fluency, and&amp;nbsp;thrives in an environment that requires both strategic thinking and hands-on execution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
