&lt;li&gt;Experience working with tools such as Jira, Zephyr, Bitbucket, GitHub, Jenkins, and Docker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated problem-solving ability — you don&#39;t stop at &quot;it failed&quot;; you dig in, connect the dots, and drive issues to resolution&lt;/li&gt;
